8>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Buying a bunch of ranger gear (fungal/thunderbolt)</span><hr size=1> It doesn't burst my bubble; I knew monks made fine MA's, I am just also aware of the capabilities of a ranger MA. However, I have to disagree to the monks with superior hitpoints, given the base stamina/hitpoint multiplier of rangers being superior to monks, as well as ranger armor generally having higher hitpoint modifiers.<br>
<br>
